Black First Land First (BLF) invites members of the media to a press conference on its registration as a political party. The media will be informed also on whether BLF is now open to all races. BLF will also clarify its stance on the 2021 Local Government Eections The media briefing will be held under the following details: Date: 05 February 2021, Friday
Time: 11h00am
Venue: outside the IEC office, Election House, Riverside Office Park,1303 Heuwel Avenue, Centurion Issued by Black First Land First, National Coordinating Committee of (BLF NCC)
2 February 2021 Contact Details: Black First Land First Mail: blackfirstlandfirst@ gmail.com
